beer.beer_description:
Santa threw a sackful of German ingredients including malt, Tettnang, and Hallertau Hops, and German Lager Yeast to create this classic Oktoberfest beer.

Deep orange in colour with a light malt aroma, Santa has swapped his sleigh for a stein and is celebrating like only the Germans know how! So get your Oom-Pah on and celebrate Christmas in Oktober!
